../../../exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/judgments/chain-02.md:5:The attacker is mostly right. The original chain points at a real mission-aligned pressure point: exact Navier-Stokes may realize some desired Tao-role channels while still failing to isolate them. But the chain treated "leakage" as if it could be chosen by bookkeeping, delayed the geometry and helicity adversary too long, and moved too quickly from forced couplings to a dynamical obstruction claim.
