../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-03.md:41:### Step 3 - Stress-test one rigidity route against Tao's barrier
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-03.md:49:- The instruction to test whether a route uses "exact NS structure rather than only compactness plus harmonic analysis" is right in spirit but vague in practice. Many arguments use the NS equation explicitly while still providing no genuine leverage beyond Tao-preserved structure. The chain needs a sharper criterion than rhetorical NS-specificity.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-03.md:50:- Tao's barrier is treated as a binary filter, but the relevant question is quantitative: does the rigidity route exploit a monotone quantity, sign structure, epsilon-regularity mechanism, or unique continuation input that survives the scaling and compactness regime of the minimal element? Without that refinement, the memo may only restate "this still looks too harmonic-analytic."
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-03.md:51:- The kill condition is again too compressed. A route can fail for reasons other than collapsing to Tao-preserved structure: wrong solution class, no time directionality, non-closedness under limits, incompatibility with almost-periodic scaling, or the need for extra decay that a critical element will not have.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-03.md:128:If this chain is kept, it should be judged almost entirely by the quality of its obstruction map. A positive program should only be credited if it identifies a rigidity mechanism that is not merely Navier-Stokes-flavored in wording, but demonstrably limit-stable, phase-space-compatible, and stronger than the generic structures Tao's barrier already preserves.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:7:Its real strengths should be preserved: it asks for estimate-level gains, rejects identity-level cosmetics, and is willing to end with a negative memo. Its real weaknesses also need repair: it does not fix the architecture sharply enough, leaves the Tao screen too verbal, treats geometry/tensor effects too much as contamination, and makes the negative endpoint easier to earn than the positive one.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:27:### 3. The Tao screen is conceptually right but operationally too weak
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:31:This is the central criticism. It is not enough to say that a candidate uses an "exact NS feature." The branch needs an explicit statement of what Tao-style averaging destroys, and where that loss should appear in the localized estimate.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:57:But this does not make the branch redundant. It still has value if it fixes one exact localized estimate, states what new bookkeeping or Tao-relevant comparison is being tested, and then closes the loophole cleanly.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:79:This lands. A "concrete proposition" is not enough unless the chain says what proof architecture it feeds and what quantitative benchmark counts as a material improvement. The final claim also has to stay narrow: at best this branch can certify that a specified reformulation family fails to produce a Tao-relevant gain within one fixed architecture.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:87:3. Replace the loose Tao filter with an explicit NS-versus-averaged discriminator.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/judgments/chain-01.md:98:Most of that probability lies on a clean, publishable obstruction memo: a sharply delimited statement that a specified family of exact NS reformulations does not create a Tao-relevant gain on one fixed localized bottleneck except possibly through hybrid geometry/tensor effects that belong in another branch. The chance of a genuinely positive lead is lower, but not zero once one tightly controlled paired route is still allowed.
