../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/mission-context.md:39:This is NOT "try random approaches and hope." The Tao constraint gives us a precise filter: the property must distinguish the actual NS nonlinearity from the averaged version. The SQG success gives us a concrete example of what "using the right structural property" looks like.
