../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:82:The planner says Tao's averaged-NS filter is mandatory. This chain does not operationalize that soon enough. It allows a long audit of weak-type packaging before forcing the question whether the package is anything more than preserved harmonic analysis.
