../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/attacks/chain-03.md:107:The most likely earned output is a negative result of the form: once De Giorgi recursion is forbidden, the remaining weak-type package either collapses under localization, reduces to strong-type control, or stays inside Tao-compatible generic harmonic analysis. That would still be useful. But it means the chain should be viewed primarily as a cleanup operation on one lingering mission lead, not as a strong forward route to regularity.
