../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:5:The attacker is mostly right. The original chain is disciplined and worth keeping, but only as a narrowly scoped obstruction branch, not as a broad discovery program for the mission's beyond-De-Giorgi mechanism. Its main strengths are real: it asks for estimate-level gains, it front-loads killing cosmetic rewrites, and it is willing to end negatively. Its main weaknesses are also real: it leaves the target architecture under-specified, states the Tao screen too loosely, treats geometry too much as contamination, and makes the negative endpoint easier to earn than the positive one.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:7:The correct refinement is to fix one inherited estimate architecture at the start, define the gain in one bookkeeping currency, require an explicit Tao discriminator, and treat this branch as a bounded test of whether exact NS reformulations or one tightly specified paired auxiliary quantity can beat the named bottleneck. If not, the obstruction memo is the intended success case.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:19:### 2. The Tao screen is conceptually right but operationally too weak
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:23:This is a central flaw. "Not obviously preserved by Tao's averaged model" is too loose. The refined chain needs a concrete statement of what exact NS feature is supposed to fail in the averaged setting and where that failure enters the localized estimate.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:47:This concern is real but not fatal. The project already knows that the vorticity route hits the same `beta = 4/3` barrier and that Beltrami cancellation is fragile. Retesting those directions is only justified if the refined chain states exactly what new localized estimate, commutator accounting, or Tao-relevant comparison is being added.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:94:4. Replace the loose Tao filter with an explicit NS-versus-averaged discriminator.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/judgments/chain-01.md:104:Most of that probability lies on a useful negative result: a disciplined memo showing that, within one fixed estimate architecture and a tightly defined candidate family, exact NS reformulations do not produce a Tao-relevant gain except possibly through geometry-dominated or architecture-changing effects. The chance of a genuinely positive lead remains materially lower, but not zero once the chain allows one tightly controlled auxiliary-quantity route.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/final-decider.md:5:The winning chain is **Refined Chain 01 - Harmonic Tail Obstruction Test with Early Tao Gate**.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/final-decider.md:20:Chain 01 has the clearest near-term endpoint: either it finds an NS-specific way to shrink the far-field pressure coefficient, or it produces a sharp obstruction memo showing that local harmonic-tail structure cannot do that in a Tao-relevant way. That is a much cleaner finish line than the likely outcomes of Chains 02 or 03.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/final-decider.md:39:- early Tao gate
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/final-decider.md:51:Chain 01's novelty ceiling is lower, but not trivial. If an NS-specific harmonic-tail mechanism survives both the shell model and the Tao screen, that would still be a real structural find. More importantly, the floor is much stronger, and the decision criteria explicitly reward that.
