../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:5:The attacker is mostly right. The original chain had a real discriminator: whether exact Navier-Stokes triad geometry contains structure that a Tao-style averaging would wash out. It also had better kill conditions than many speculative Fourier-symbol routes. But it still allowed too much freedom before committing to a proof-relevant bottleneck, and that makes it too easy to generate attractive symbolic memos without earning theorem-level leverage.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:7:The right repair is not to discard the chain. It is to make it bottleneck-first and obstruction-first. A positive branch should survive only if one exact triad feature can be written as an explicit candidate inequality for one fixed estimate and still remain useful after shell summation, mixed-helicity restoration, and any required localization.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:17:### 2. The Tao comparator and the test for "real structure" are under-specified
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:21:The attacker is correct that "Tao-sensitive" can become rhetorical unless the comparison class is fixed precisely. The original chain also did not give a sufficiently invariant test for whether a feature is structural rather than representational. The refined chain keeps the comparator, but only as an operational check relative to a fixed target estimate.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:33:This criticism lands. Same-helicity preference, Beltrami depletion language, and restricted-interaction folklore are well known failure modes in this area. A mechanism that only survives on a thin or already familiar class should not be promoted. The refined chain therefore requires the prior-art comparison and, if a restricted class is used, a quantified statement of how much of the relevant transfer or shell sum that class actually carries.
../../../beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-006/judgments/chain-02.md:39:The original chain knew where the graveyard was, but it treated those items too much like a later stress test. In reality they are the main proof obligations. The refined version makes reconstruction explicit: shell summation, angular multiplicity, mixed-helicity contamination, nonlocal interactions, and localization losses all have to be charged before anything is called live.
