planning-runs/run-007/planner.md:28:Central premise: the real NS nonlinearity moves both energy and helicity, and the joint transfer geometry may be stronger than the energy-only or triad-only pictures already audited. A live mechanism would have to survive full mixed-helicity restoration and yield a theorem-relevant depletion or no-bad-cascade statement.
planning-runs/run-007/planner.md:30:Why it belongs now: it is the cleanest untouched invariant route that is neither the dead LEI rewrite audit nor the old symbol-first triad ledger.
planning-runs/run-007/planner.md:34:Central premise: viscosity does not erase transport structure completely; it converts Kelvin/Cauchy-style identities into stochastic transport statements. If Tao-style averaging destroys the adapted stochastic backbone, this could be an NS-specific route unavailable to purely harmonic-analysis methods.
