+- Execution decision after the receptionist:
+  - run three bounded explorations, because the step still needs source-backed
+    artifacts even though the likely verdict is negative;
+  - `exploration-001` freezes the scope lock and tests whether the baseline and
+    gain threshold can be made concrete enough to avoid immediate setup
