+
+- Launched `exploration-001` through `bin/launch-role.sh` with sentinel
+  `explorations/exploration-001/REPORT-SUMMARY.md`.
+- Read the summary and full report after the sentinel landed.
+- Main result adopted:
+  - one narrowed provisional setup is locally supportable:
+    `stretching/enstrophy bottleneck` +
+    `dyadic coupled fluxes` +
+    packet-level Tao screen;
+  - but the baseline criterion is still only burden-language and the minimum
+    gain threshold is still only `positive margin after debts`, so the setup is
