+- Operational consequence:
+  - treat `setup obstruction` as already live unless the invariant-ledger and
+    Tao-calibration exploration can somehow sharpen the missing baseline/gain
+    currency;
+  - continue with `exploration-002` because Step 11 still requires the exact
