+  freeze one exact bad term or bad transfer pattern inside the stretching/enstrophy burden language.
+  state one explicit baseline inequality, exclusion statement, or contradiction line and one gain currency that later steps must beat.
+
+- Unexpected findings:
+  the strongest Tao-sensitive feature on disk is not generic same-helicity folklore but packet-level role bookkeeping with mandatory conjugate completion, frozen helical sign sheets, and spectator-leakage control.
+  the local record is already explicit that the branch is stronger as an obstruction audit than as a positive route.
