+  invariant package: `dyadic coupled fluxes` `[INFERRED]`
+  Tao-sensitive feature: role-labeled helical packet coupling with mandatory conjugate completion and frozen packet-sheet data, screened by the five-part Tao canonicalization test `[INFERRED]`
