+- `library/factual/navier-stokes/helical-signs-amplitude-normalization-and-phase-anchor-belong-to-the-frozen-packet-sheet.md`
+
+## Output Requirements
+
+Write:
+
+- `REPORT.md`
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md`
+
+Keep the result scope-lock-first and obstruction-honest. The point is to freeze
+or kill the branch's setup, not to narrate invariant geometry attractively.
