+
+- `[VERIFIED]` The strongest exact on-disk law is the Fourier/Leray evolution:
+
+  ```text
+  ∂t û(k) + |k|^2 û(k)
+    = -i ∑_{p+q=k} (q·û(p)) P_k û(q),
